{"tid":426954,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［跟三上拍動作片］日AV公司到台徵100名「A片男主角」","createTime":"2017-10-07T05:52:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-07T06:39:27.000Z","uid":41351,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"88fb73019e2e31d073836a793b43c9de5f5270c8","tid":426954,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T05:52:58.000Z","msg":"有網友昨（28日）晚間在臉書《報廢公社》PO出一張徵才訊息，只見內容提到誠徵「A片男主角100位」，並列出多項基本條件，引起許多男網友暴動，不過也有眼尖的網友發現公告寫明「不支薪、不含勞健保」紛紛笑說不過就是「汁男而已！」<br />\n<br />\n照片上的徵才訊息寫道，「強烈性飢渴者為佳，對男女雙修、陰陽調和有基本認知，具有要硬就硬的氣魄與能力，10月3日可開始出班者」」最後並強調「限額一百位，不支薪、不含勞健保，未滿18歲請回頭是岸。」<br />\n<br />\n徵才訊息曝光後引起網友熱議，紛紛留言回應「先報名了！」、「這頂多汁男而已吧？」、「專業體液交換員」、「哇～虧大了，這份工作沒收入就算了，還要兩億兩億地倒貼！」不過據了解，該則徵才訊息是成人頻道「潘朵啦Pandora」為了最新的VR平台所釋出的廣告訊息。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://gotv.ctitv.com.tw/2017/09/687848.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgotv.ctitv.com.tw%2F2017%2F09%2F687848.htm&d=C7tQ6xEAOqYXcbV8vwRrwv%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=6ac16078\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://gotv.ctitv.com.tw/2017/09/687848.htm</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/07/135236_c156a46dc3d551acef60b066a891ea94.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F07%2F135236_c156a46dc3d551acef60b066a891ea94.jpg&h=8be47b0b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/07/135237_c156a46dc3d551acef60b066a891ea94.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F07%2F135237_c156a46dc3d551acef60b066a891ea94.jpg&h=63f3ebaa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港男可以飛台一試"},{"pid":"2b0a1734cd5c35e3ea33682918c8e0d10d52fb70","tid":426954,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T05:57:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/07/135746_9595b03e1bcab3015b7f3ebfa14b3a89.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F07%2F135746_9595b03e1bcab3015b7f3ebfa14b3a89.jpg&h=dcb11fcb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n辛苦工"},{"pid":"db0ba9494b8fe462886e88d93f249ad253a931d6","tid":426954,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T05:58:46.000Z","msg":"假嘅"},{"pid":"1de98975b4ccd947c7a28820ceae2d3543359e2d","tid":426954,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T05:59:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3db7520ee2bec399292e1dfb3aeed34acf420bed","tid":426954,"uid":3549,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T06:07:48.000Z","msg":"義工"},{"pid":"b71c298cba61ced97c5e442846695ee3956a62e2","tid":426954,"uid":118120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T06:16:40.000Z","msg":"汁男 / 男男做 0 果個 / 玩屎玩尿果d 核突野 / 屌七十路果類重口味<br />\n<br />\n自己揀 <br />\n<br />\n有得屌靚女人地點會咁好益外人"},{"pid":"d35007bf919852ed4edecaccf22bf807c3a1eaec","tid":426954,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T06:39:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>汁男 / 男男做 0 果個 / 玩屎玩尿果d 核突野 / 屌七十路果類重口味<br />\n<br />\n自己揀 <br />\n<br />\n有得屌靚女人地點會咁好益外人</blockquote><br />\n如果貼錢幾千蚊港紙有冇可能"}]}